# Configuring SQL Server for Develop
## Installation on Ubuntu

Install:

    sudo apt install postgresql postgresql-contrib

Start:

    pg_ctlcluster 12 main start

Create new user role:
    
    sudo -u postgres createuser --interactive

Choose finance_updater as name

Create db:

    sudo -u postgres createdb finance_updater
    sudo -u postgres createdb finance

Create user:

    sudo adduser finance_updater

Choose password of your choice

Connect using new user:

    sudo -u finance_updater psql -d finance

Check connection info with:

    \conninfo

    